nodes.text: Star Wars Adventures: Return to Vader's Castle

Star Wars Adventures: Return to Vader's Castle is a canon comic book series written by Cavan Scott. It was published during October 2019. The stories featured Darth Maul, Asajj Ventress, Jabba the Hutt, Darth Vader, and Grand Moff Tarkin.
